description: Number of partitions of n into distinct odd parts, the least being 3.
links: Charles R Greathouse IV, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
prog: (PARI)N=99;x='x+O('x^N);t=sum(n=2,N,x^(n^2-1)/prod(k=1,n-2,1-x^(2*k))); /* == x^3 + x^8 + x^10 + ... */v=Vec(t) /* show terms for n>=3 */  /* Joerg Arndt, Jan 29 2011 */
author: _Clark Kimberling_
